  heading={'Save Money & Improve Comfort'}
  body={'Energy-saving window film provides a range of benefits for homes and businesses in Philadelphia, including: Save an average of 30% during summer and 10%-15% during winter Eliminate hold/cold spots Improve comfort while lowering energy costs Insulate existing glass doors and windows Reject solar heat and UV radiation Cost-effective alternative to window replacement For more information, check out these resources: 3m_Prestige_Film_Case_Study_Philadelphia 3M_Sun_Control_Film_Case_Study_Philadelphia Energy_Saving_Window_Film_Philadelphia_Case_Study Source of Energy Saving Window Film Philadelphia'}
